2026-04-16 20:47:05 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': '我收到任务了。先按流程检查任务单完整性：\n\n| 检查项 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| 功能描述 | ✅ | 中文自然语言→结构化日历事件 |\n| 输入/输出格式 | ✅ | 有输入示例和输出 JSON 结构 |\n| 验收标准（DoD） | ✅ | 6条明确标准，含准确率、性能、覆盖要求 |\n| 技术约束 | ✅ | ≤1秒且不含网络请求（隐含排除外部API），按团队约定 Python 3.10+ |\n\nDoD 完整，可以进入技术设计。先加载 SOP 获取设计规范。', 'reasoning_content': "Let me analyze this task carefully:\n\n1. I'm a Dev (Senior Developer) - my job is to produce a technical design document (tech_design.md)\n2. The task is to design a NLP parsing module for Chinese natural language schedule input\n3. I need to follow my SOP: load sop_dev skill → complete technical design → write output to workspace\n\nLet me first load the sop_dev skill to get the design specification, then produce the tech_design.md.\n\nLet me check the task completeness first:\n- 功能描述: ✅ Clear - NLP parsing module for Chinese natural language to structured calendar events\n- 输入/输出格式: ✅ Input examples and output format provided\n- 验收标准: ✅ 6 clear acceptance criteria\n- 技术约束: Partially - performance constraint (≤1s, no network) is implied, language is Python per team convention\n\nThe DoD is clear, so I can proceed with the design.\n\nLet me load the sop_dev skill first.", 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "sop_dev", "task_context": ""}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-8c2421bcc5dd43b9866b0a38d8295ef8', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 3949, 'completion_tokens': 376, 'total_tokens': 4325, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 207}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'created': 1776343626, 'system_fingerprint': None, 'model': 'glm-5.1', 'id': 'chatcmpl-e1ba974e-60ee-9454-99fc-c8f48675a918'}
